I’m 20 

Female 

107 pounds 

medications: birth control 
never been diagnosed with anxiety or depression but I went to therapy for some anxious thoughts I was having. I don’t have any other health problems except sometimes I have no appetite and I struggle with neck pain.  

I’m not sure if I should have posted this in an another thread but about 3-4 times a week, I wake up around 4ish and go back to sleep to later wake up at 7. Some of the time I can remember waking up because of a nightmare or an incredibly vivid dream. This has been happening for about a year. It doesn’t bother me that much but it’s kinda annoying to wake up every night. I’m always surprised that I slept through the night because I usually don’t. 
I’m not sure if it’s connected to anxiety or something... since I’m having nightmares so often but yeah not totally sure.
